# Project CLAUDE.md is kept local-only (holds prod test-account creds) — never commit
/CLAUDE.md
# AGENTS.md is a local symlink → CLAUDE.md (gitignored). A tracked symlink to a
# gitignored target dangles on a fresh CI checkout, and electron-builder's signed
# `--mac` file walk stat()s it → ENOENT, breaking the release build. Keep local-only.
/AGENTS.md

